  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>[emote=Inspired]Wow![pause=20] [color=#FFC663]Wishmaker Cave[color] is so beautiful![br][emote=Normal]Sometimes, I feel something stirring in me when I look at the crystals.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK2" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>I could have sworn I saw something shiny in the ground earlier.[br][emote=Worried]I wish I could remember where I last saw it...</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK3" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Heh.[pause=0] These crystals can't hide from old [color=#00F8F8]Zangoose[color].[br][emote=Normal]Hidden from the plain eye, I know they're hidden.... </value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK4" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>[emote=Pain]Ughh, those [color=#00F8F8]Tentacools[color] are nasty, [pause=20]very nasty.[br][emote=Pain]I don't know why,[pause=20] but I feel absolutely horrible after fighting one.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK5" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Huh,[pause=20] I noticed some Pokémon here actively seek crystals to become more powerful.[br]I think it's best to use their power immediately the moment you find them.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK6" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Rumor has it,[pause=10] something rests within the depths of this cave.[br]...Waiting to be awaken by explorers who hold their wishes until the very end. </value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK7.0" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>{0} more[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10] Like a star[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]\nFor [color=#F8F800]Wishmaker[color].</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK7.1" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>[emote=Happy]Like a star[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10] Hold until the end.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=20]\nFor [color=#F8F800]Wishmaker[color].</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK8" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>One arduous journey.[pause=0] The collective star power of gems.[pause=0] And one single wish.[br][emote=Happy]My masterpiece will soon be finished!</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK9" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]Explorers,[pause=30] when you reach the depths,[pause=30] place your gems in a formation of a star[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[br]The more gems,[pause=30] the greater you shall reap the reward.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="WISHMAKER_NPC_TALK10" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]Hold your wishes until the end.[pause=0]\nFor [color=#F8F800]Wishmaker[color].</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10][emote=happy]</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_END_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10][emote=happy]Best wishes.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_PAY_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]Total is {0}.[pause=10]\nDeal?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_PAY_DONE_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10][emote=happy]Thank you.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_PAY_REFUSE_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_PAY_SHORT_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]Need more money.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_SELL_0003" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.[pause=10].[pause=10].[pause=10]I give {0}.[pause=10]\nAgree?</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TALK_SHOP_SELL_DONE_0003" xml:space="preserve">
